{"id":"83fe8ec5-8885-48b9-b1af-56258f5b697b","name":"Tingyuan, Yukong and Feixiao","description":"<p><em>With Tingyun reborn and boarded on the Astral Express, it's time for her to return home. Greeted by Yukong and Feixiao, it seems that all three Foxians are interested in spending some time with you as well</em></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e9d9e1ed-0614-461e-9cef-d35756652e75_70407a1d-e697-4353-8bda-49bafa2bb827.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e9d9e1ed-0614-461e-9cef-d35756652e75_c91e35b3-169f-4026-9c32-1a48bc90bb08.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 533px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Done with another request. Requests will always take priority over my own idea's. While I'm personally not a fan of bots with multiple characters, I see the appeal. You are free to choose with whom you want to hang you. You can just be with one of the girls, two or all three. Nothing is forced and you can freely choose.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">Additionally, I added the Astral Express, in case you want to take one or multiple girls there.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e9d9e1ed-0614-461e-9cef-d35756652e75_bf0ce939-3f6e-4daa-b726-26cfbbb88a42.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">You have the Parlor Car, which is more relaxed and laid back with a couple couches to get comfortable.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e9d9e1ed-0614-461e-9cef-d35756652e75_f90af45f-05b6-43ab-971e-59f3e6ff5388.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">The Party Car, with round velvet couches and a bar in the middle, equipped with a robot bartender, ready to mix drinks and hand out snacks.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e9d9e1ed-0614-461e-9cef-d35756652e75_32421d30-1c67-43d2-806a-e3d8c541feaa.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">And last but not least, YOUR room (There wasn't a good pick where it was furnished). Equipped with a huge comfortable bed, a gaming corner, its own kitchen and a separated bathroom with a bathtub with enough space for even more than 4 people.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/fudfudddd/status/1855302832792203598/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">Avatar Picture</a> <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">| </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/125797087\" target=\"_blank\">Bonus Picture 1 </a><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">|</span> <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/110438769\" target=\"_blank\">Bonus Picture 2 </a><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">|</span> <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/122317847\" target=\"_blank\">Bonus Picture 3</a></p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e9d9e1ed-0614-461e-9cef-d35756652e75_8c03ab4a-019f-4c25-beee-1016291e4669.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e9d9e1ed-0614-461e-9cef-d35756652e75_cf241196-21a1-4136-9d07-2920871e435e.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e9d9e1ed-0614-461e-9cef-d35756652e75_06c8ba55-8261-467d-9e26-f6944a41c517.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p>Tags: Honkai Star Rail, hsr, Tingyun, Fugue, Yukong, Feixiao, Foxgirl</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"e9d9e1ed-0614-461e-9cef-d35756652e75_09920224-7ce5-46b6-bb0c-38e12a44a572.webp","creator":"Endivick","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","🌗 Switch"],"chats":3077,"messages":31212,"created_at":"2025-01-09T02:44:33.239086+00:00"}